272
00:16:52,678 --> 00:16:54,430
Aku tak melihat ada CCTV.

273
00:16:54,513 --> 00:16:55,472
Benar.

274
00:16:55,556 --> 00:16:59,810
Polsek setempat sudah menanyai
tiap pelanggan yang berkunjung hari itu,

275
00:16:59,893 --> 00:17:01,228
tetapi tak menemukan apa pun.

276
00:17:01,311 --> 00:17:02,855
Namun, ponselnya…

277
00:17:02,938 --> 00:17:05,065
Di peta itu, kau akan
melihat Danau Daejong.

278
00:17:05,149 --> 00:17:06,692
TOJUNG-DONG

279
00:17:07,317 --> 00:17:08,277
DANAU DAEJONG

280
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:10,654
Danau Daejong?
Itu seperti tempat rekreasi.

281
00:17:10,738 --> 00:17:13,115
Diperkirakan dia hilang
sekitar pukul 01.00,

282
00:17:13,198 --> 00:17:14,950
jadi, dia tak ke sana untuk bermain.

283
00:17:15,034 --> 00:17:16,910
Tidak ada yang terekam di CCTV.

284
00:17:16,994 --> 00:17:18,412
Apa ada kemungkinan bunuh diri?

285
00:17:18,495 --> 00:17:20,998
Para penyelam sudah mencari seluruh danau,

286
00:17:21,081 --> 00:17:22,082
tetapi nihil.

287
00:17:22,166 --> 00:17:23,459
Dia tak bunuh diri.

288
00:17:24,418 --> 00:17:25,836
Apalagi,

289
00:17:25,919 --> 00:17:27,921
orang terakhir yang bicara dengannya

290
00:17:28,005 --> 00:17:29,173
adalah anak perempuannya.

291
00:17:30,132 --> 00:17:32,968
Katanya akan membeli
ayam goreng, lalu pulang.

292
00:17:35,137 --> 00:17:37,473
Mustahil memanggil taksi di sini.

293
00:17:39,641 --> 00:17:41,518
Dia mungkin naik bus di halte itu.

294
00:17:42,269 --> 00:17:43,312
Benar.

295
00:17:43,395 --> 00:17:46,398
Kami sudah memeriksa, bahkan mewawancarai

296
00:17:46,482 --> 00:17:49,276
sopir bus terakhir malam itu,

297
00:17:50,235 --> 00:17:51,445
tetapi dia tak naik bus.

298
00:17:51,945 --> 00:17:54,740
{\an8}Selain itu, lokasi terakhirnya
yang terlacak dari ponsel

299
00:17:54,823 --> 00:17:56,784
